text: Ayoub Ouhafsa (born 14 November 1997) is a French professional footballer who plays as a forward for Rodez. ==Professional career== On 16 July 2019, Ouhafsa joined Rodez AF from Marseille II. He made his professional debut with Rodez in a 2–0 Ligue 2 win over AJ Auxerre on 26 July 2019, scoring in the first minute of the game. ==Personal life== Born in France, Ouhafsa is of Moroccan descent. ==References== ==External links== * * * FDB Profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:People from Millau Category:Association football forwards Category:French footballers Category:French people of Moroccan descent Category:Rodez AF players Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Championnat National players Category:Championnat National 2 players
